    "chunk_id": "docling_docstructbench_llm-raw-scihub-o.O-j.snb.2004.05.025.pdf_5_128",
    "text": "The apparent affinity constant between Ac-i-Trp and the formed chiral recognition site, which was constructed by the presence of i-isomer during the molecular imprinting process, was determined by the following procedure: the difference in the shift (A0)s, between that for Ac-i-Trp, which was adsorbed not only on the chiral recognition site toward i-isomer but also on the non-specific region, and that for Ac-j-Trp, which was non-specifically adsorbed, was",
